  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dc5 \u0d9c\u0d82\u0da2\u0dcf \u0dad\u0ddc\u0d9c\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person is arrested with a stock of Kerala ganja worth over one crore",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person was arrested today (20th) with 54 kilos and 710 grams of Kerala ganja worth over ten million rupees, says the Colombo South Division Criminal Investigation Unit.",
        "Police say that the arrested person is a (24)-year-old resident of Sedawatta area of \u200b\u200bWellampitiya.",
        "During this raid, the Senior Superintendent of Police in charge of Colombo South Division Mr. Sisira Pettathantri was informed about a person who was selling Kerala cannabis in bulk to many areas around Colombo. It is said that a person was arrested with the stock of Kerala ganja.",
        "While raiding and inspecting a house in Kurunduwatta Hatte Watta area, the police found three suspicious parcels hidden in that house.",
        "Later, the three parcels were taken into police custody and during inspection, they found Kerala ganja in them, and when they were weighed, the police said that there were 54 kilos of Kerala ganja and 710 grams in them.",
        "It is said that the value of the stock of Kerala ganja seized by the police is over ten million.",
        "The police said that this Kerala ganja had been smuggled in order to be sold in bulk to many areas around Colombo and earlier the Mattakkuliya police arrested the suspect along with 20 kilos of Kerala ganja and took him to jail.",
        "Investigations are on whether other people involved in the Kerala ganja trafficking of the suspect are involved.",
        "The arrested suspect was to be handed over to the Kuruduwatta police to be presented to the Maligakanda court."
      ],
